Nick Loeb has filed a lawsuit against his ex-fiancee Sofia Vergara in a bid to prevent her from destroying two cryopreserved female embryos created through IVF . 
  Loeb claims she insisted on using her 44-year-old assistant as the surrogate despite his objections . 
  The pair planned to have children with a surrogate in 2012 but split in November 2013 . 
  He also claims she was 'physically and mentally abusive' to him . 
 